OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775661069
OL,3,CInquests open into deaths of three men
OL,4,Cin crash
OL,6,FDuring the short hearing, assistant
OL,7,Fcoroner Angela Brocklehurst said West
OL,8,FYorkshire Police had requested more
OL,9,Ftime to consider any "criminal
OL,10,Factivity".
OL,12,FFour people have been arrested over
OL,13,Fthe incident but no-one has been
OL,14,Fcharged.
OL,16,FMs Brocklehurst suspended the inquest
OL,17,Funtil 7 April next year.
OL,19,FThe hearing was told that Mr Bryant
OL,20,Fand Mr Reilly were both self-employed
OL,21,Fentrepreneurs.
